#  POSITIONAL args via `arg` tag + ENV VAR fallback via `env` +
#  RUNTIME VARS via `kong.Vars{}` interpolated into defaults +
#  CUSTOM MAPPERS via `kong.NewMapper`/`kong.NamedMapper` for
#  custom type parsers + INTERFACE-BASED `Run(ctx) error` dispatch
#  on subcommand structs (CONTRAST cobra's Run/RunE func fields) —
#  corpus's **first formally documented kingpin-successor struct-
#  tag Go CLI library**.  Brings cross-language CLI library
#  taxonomy variant count to 153; Go ecosystem now has 13
#  documented CLI libraries — TYING WITH RUST at the top of the
